title: Mini Series - State v. John Brookins - Episode 1 - Right Place, Wrong Time
description:
September 14, 2020 / The Undisclosed team investigates the case of John Brookins, who was convicted of the 1990 murder of Sheila Ginsberg in Bucks County, Pennsylvania.

Episode scoring music by Animal Weapon and Blue Dot Sessions.
